Hey people :wave::skin-tone-4:

I'm Sonia, from Lagos, and I'm currently navigating the choppy waters of content marketing at a B2C early-stage start-up. I also dedicate about 15 hours per week to freelance writing gigs, so hit me up if you need a hand (and a pen).

Excited to be here and I can't wait to learn, share, and grow with everyone!
